  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Place the treacle, coconut milk, ginger, lime juice, sugar, butter, cilantro, coconut oil, salt, cumin, and black pepper in a blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Pour the mixture into a dolsot stoneware bowl and place it in the oven.",
    "Bake for 12 minutes, or until the treacle is bubbly and slightly caramelized.",
    "Serve the treacle bowl hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
